OL,3,CIllegal worker says digital IDs will
OL,4,Cnot stop immigrants coming to UK to
OL,5,Cwork
OL,7,FITV News Correspondent Jonathan Brown
OL,8,Fspeaks to asylum seekers earning as
OL,9,Flittle as #5 an hour in Bolton about
OL,10,Fhow they accept the risks of working
OL,11,Fillegally, despite police increasing
OL,12,Fimmigration status checks in the town.
OL,14,FThe fast food strapped to his bike has
OL,15,Fgone cold because the delivery rider
OL,16,Fwe see stopped by immigration
OL,17,Fofficials on a back street in Bolton
OL,18,Fis an asylum seeker.
