OL,3,CIllegal worker says digital IDs will
OL,4,Cnot stop immigrants coming to UK to
OL,5,Cwork
OL,7,FThe man, who is originally from
OL,8,FPakistan, does not have the legal
OL,9,Fright to work in the UK, having
OL,10,Fcrossed the Channel in a small boat in
OL,11,FMarch this year.
OL,13,FThe Home Office immigration
OL,14,Fenforcement officer we are shadowing
OL,15,Ftells him that his arrest could count
OL,16,Fagainst his claim to remain in the
OL,17,Fcountry.
