OL,3,CIllegal worker says digital IDs will
OL,4,Cnot stop immigrants coming to UK to
OL,5,Cwork
OL,7,FHe is one of an increasing number of
OL,8,Fmigrants being caught illegally
OL,9,Fworking in the UK, prompting the Home
OL,10,FOffice to invite us on a special joint
OL,11,Foperation with Greater Manchester
OL,12,FPolice.
OL,14,FIn a new approach, we saw police stop
OL,15,Fdelivery riders in Bolton town centre
OL,16,Fto test the roadworthiness of their
OL,17,Fbikes, while immigration officers
OL,18,Fchecked their documents - this drew
OL,19,Fcrowds but no illegal workers.
