OL,3,CIllegal worker says digital IDs will
OL,4,Cnot stop immigrants coming to UK to
OL,5,Cwork
OL,7,FBut we have spoken to one man, who
OL,8,Fwished to remain anonymous, about how
OL,9,Fhe is willing to risk being caught
OL,10,Fworking illegally because he is so
OL,11,Fdesperate to earn a living.
OL,13,FHe is seeking asylum in the UK -
OL,14,Fclaiming he was tortured in his home
OL,15,Fcountry in South Asia over his
OL,16,Fpolitical views - and is being paid
OL,17,Fcash-in-hand at a takeaway in Northern
OL,18,FEngland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
