OL,3,CIllegal worker says digital IDs will
OL,4,Cnot stop immigrants coming to UK to
OL,5,Cwork
OL,7,FThe man, who we are calling Rovin, is
OL,8,Fpaid #5 per hour - less than half the
OL,9,Fminimum wage - to work casual shifts.
OL,11,F"I don't want to work illegally I know
OL,12,Fit's a crime, I know. I don't have
OL,13,Foption," He tells me. "If not working,
OL,14,Fhow can I eat?"
OL,16,FRovin, who has been waiting 16 months
OL,17,Ffor the result of his asylum claim,
OL,18,Flives with a relative and gets around
OL,19,F#50 per week from the government to
OL,20,Flive off.
