OL,3,CIllegal worker says digital IDs will
OL,4,Cnot stop immigrants coming to UK to
OL,5,Cwork
OL,7,FAsylum seekers like him have no legal
OL,8,Fright to work during their first 12
OL,9,Fmonths in the UK - after that, some
OL,10,Fcan, but only in specific professions
OL,11,F- Rovin's trade as a chef isn't one of
OL,12,Fthem.
OL,14,FHe tells me he knows other asylum
OL,15,Fseekers who are working 12-hour days
OL,16,Fin factories, newsagents and
OL,17,Frestaurants for as little as #4 per
OL,18,Fhour.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
