OL,3,CIllegal worker says digital IDs will
OL,4,Cnot stop immigrants coming to UK to
OL,5,Cwork
OL,7,F"They take (businesses) advantage," he
OL,8,Fsaid. "We are not, we are suffering.
OL,9,FWe will not take any advantage. We
OL,10,Fneed to survive. We are survivor."
