OL,3,CIllegal worker says digital IDs will
OL,4,Cnot stop immigrants coming to UK to
OL,5,Cwork
OL,7,FHe added that he does not believe
OL,8,Fdigital IDs mooted by the government
OL,9,Fwill put off immigrants from coming to
OL,10,Fthe UK and trying to work, or
OL,11,Funscrupulous businesses from paying
OL,12,Fthem.
OL,14,F"If they give us permission to work
OL,15,Ffor every sector, (we) no need to
OL,16,Ftheir money," he said. "The government
OL,17,Fwaste money."
