OL,7,FThe Home Office says it has made
OL,8,Faround 7,000 arrests over illegal
OL,9,Fworking in the year to July last year,
OL,10,Fwhich is a 50 per cent increase on the
OL,11,Fyear prior.
OL,13,FMore than 2,000 penalty notices have
OL,14,Fbeen issued to businesses hiring
OL,15,Fillegal workers in that time.
OL,17,FMel Hindle, the Home Office's chief
OL,18,Fimmigration officer for the North
OL,19,FWest, told us: "We could be about
OL,20,Fprobably seven days a week now.
